                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17201207-35-off187 t17201207-35-crimeloc189"></join>, and that he got a Warrant to search, and found the Hay in Mr. Honer's Stable. Mr. Honer deposed, that he met the Prisoner at a Publick House, and agreed with him to serve his Horse and Coult in his absence (he being going into the Country) and order'd his Servant to deliver him the Key of his Stable. His Servant deposed that he deliver'd the said Key to the Prisoner a Fortnight before the Hay was owned. 
